Bordasen<br>
High Priest<br>
Second Covenant <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulittlecherub.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Little Cherub</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cyber Pimp</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/6/01 8:32:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hi everyone</span><hr size=1> Just start using the calendar to sign up for hate and fear raids.  You'll meet lots of people that way and start making friends you'll know for the rest of your EQ career. <p><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
