     After following this thread, there are a few questions which I am asking....<br>
<br>
1)  Have you been on any planer raids?  You can get A lot of armor from Hate.  The pruple Barney Armor (etheral mist)  With the amount of that armor that drops in hate it is very easy for you to have full Planer armor within 4 or 5 raids.  Not sure exactly how much Wis or other stats a full set will give, but it is an improvement over what you currently have, and best of all it is free.<br>
<br>
2)  Does your guild have a spell bank?  Most guilds have a spell bank in which you can draw what you need from there and contribute spells as well as they drop.<br>
<br>
3) Have you considered joining another guild which can help you gather more spells and equipment?<br>
<br>
Sheesh I have given away like 6 celestial heal spells.   If you want some of the 50-54 spells I generally get a few when I am in Seb and would gladly give you a few of them...  usually just give to guild bank anyhow so is no biggie.<br>
